 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Software Engineer IPVideo Bay Shore, NY Software Engineer (Bay Shore, NY, Bridgeport, CT) 
IPVideo is currently seeking a Software Engineer to become part of a team which is responsible for supporting our suite of products including the HALO Smart Sensor, ViewScan, and AVfusion enterprise software. The position is located at our Long Island Bay Shore facility and our Bridgeport, CT facility. 
IPVideo Corporation harnesses the power of IoT and incorporates artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning to deliver a range of open platform physical security, sensor, weapons detection, and audio/visual solutions that provide maximum flexibility, performance, ease-of-use, and value. We design and manufacture solutions for a smarter and safer world! IPVideo Corporation is a subsidiary of Advance Convergence Group. 
Responsibilities include: 
Design/code/test/maintain software with a team or individually 
Work on improving an existing codebase 
Scope out and plan projects 
Work with external technology partners and vendors 
